T15TD4328E:99b-1: bra dzny'a sha ti ka n'a ma pra ka ra na /
T15TD4328E:99b-3: shes rab brgya pa zhes bya ba'i rab tu byed pa /
T15TD4328E:99b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T15TD4328E:99b-5: gang zhig legs par rtogs pa yis //
T15TD4328E:99b-6: mi rnams shes rab brgya bskyed pa //
T15TD4328E:99b-7: don gyi bstan bcos lugs dag gi /'byung gnas chen por rab tu bshad //
T15TD4328E:99b-8: mkhas pas don gyi bstan bcos las //
T15TD4328E:99b-9: dngos po gang dag gzigs gyur pa //
T15TD4328E:99b-10: de dag yi ge mang po yis //
T15TD4328E:99b-12: yi ge nyung la don mang ba //
T15TD4328E:99b-13: gtan tshigs sna tshogs rnams kyis brgyan //
T15TD4328E:99b-14: 'di ni tshigs su bcad pa brgya //
T15TD4328E:99b-15: shes rab brgya pa zhes bya'o //
T15TD4328E:99b-16: mthong dang ma mthong yon tan 'di //
T15TD4328E:99b-17: kun gyi rtsa ba shes rab yin //
T15TD4328E:99b-18: de ltar gnyis ka bsgrub pa'i phyir //
T15TD4328E:99b-19: shes rab yongs su gzung bar bya //
T15TD4328E:99b-20: chos don 'dod dang thar pa yi //
T15TD4328E:99b-21: 'byung gnas chen po rig pa yin //
T15TD4328E:99b-22: de ltas dang por gus pa yis //
T15TD4328E:99b-23: shes rab yum chen gzung bar bya //
T15TD4328E:99b-24: shes rab ldan pa gcig rgya yang //
T15TD4328E:99b-26: dor thabs ldan pa'i lus chung yang //
T15TD4328E:99b-27: mtshan dang ldan pas yo mi brnyas //
T15TD4328E:99b-28: shes rab kyis ni lus bsrungs la //
T15TD4328E:99b-29: dgra yi tshogs kyis ci byar yod //
T15TD4328E:100a-2: char gyi rgyun gyis rdzi ba med //
T15TD4328E:100a-3: shas rab rtsal dang bral ba ni //
T15TD4328E:100a-4: gzhan gyi bran byed kho nar zad //
T15TD4328E:100a-5: glang chen ri brtsegs lta bu yi //
T15TD4328E:100a-6: lus dang ldan pa snang ba bzhin //
T15TD4328E:100a-7: shes rab mig phye rnams la ni //
T15TD4328E:100a-9: lag na mar me thogs pa yi //
T15TD4328E:100a-10: mdun na mun pa med pa bzhin //
T15TD4328E:100a-11: shes rab med pa'i phun sum tshogs //
T15TD4328E:100a-12: gnam babs bzhin du byung ba lang //
T15TD4328E:100a-13: skad cig kho nas de dag med //
T15TD4328E:100a-14: mdungs pa rnams bshes pa bzhin //
T15TD4328E:100a-15: legs par brtags te byed pa la //
T15TD4328E:100a-16: ma rungs pa dag mi snang ste //
T15TD4328E:100a-17: 'phrod pa za ba'i lus la ni //
T15TD4328E:100a-18: nad kyi bar chad mi 'byung ngo //
T15TD4328E:100a-20: shes nyen yod de mkhas pa //
T15TD4328E:100a-21: chu yis gang ba'i mtsho la ni //
T15TD4328E:100a-22: mkha' la rgyu ba rnams kyang brten //
T15TD4328E:100a-23: gang zhig nyen dang 'brel ba yi //
T15TD4328E:100a-24: nor de yang ni ci ru rung //
T15TD4328E:100a-25: sprul gyi mgo la 'dug pa yi //
T15TD4328E:100a-26: nor bu la ni su zhig reg / rang don bsgrub par bya ba rnams //
T15TD4328E:100a-27: bag med las kyis bsgrub mi bya //
T15TD4328E:100a-28: sprul so shin tu gdug pa yis //
T15TD4328E:100a-29: don ma bsgrubs par phung bar snang //
T15TD4328E:100a-30: rang don bsgrub par bya ba rnams //
T15TD4328E:100a-31: bag dang bcas pa'i las kyis bsgrub //
T15TD4328E:100a-32: srin bu bad pa dzon can lus //
T15TD4328E:100a-33: khrag 'thungs bzhin du mi mthong ngo //
T15TD4328E:100a-35: gzhan gyi phan la brtson par bya //
T15TD4328E:100a-36: gting 'dzugs sbyor ba ma byas pa'i //
T15TD4328E:100a-37: sgrub pa po yis ci mi 'grub //
T15TD4328E:100a-38: gzhan gyi phyogs gzhom 'dod pas kyang //
T15TD4328E:100a-39: bdag nyid yon tan ldan par bya //
T15TD4328E:100a-40: gzhu ni rgyud dang mi ldan pa'i //
T15TD4328E:100a-41: mdas lta gang du phyin par 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:100a-42: dbri mkhyud med par smra ba dang //
T15TD4328E:100a-43: ji skad smras bzhin sgrub pa dang //
T15TD4328E:100a-44: chas bzhi nyams dang sbyor ba yi //
T15TD4328E:100a-45: mi pho rnams ni bde bar 'tsho //
T15TD4328E:100a-46: ya rabs rnams kyi spod pa la //
T15TD4328E:100a-47: skye bo ngan pas gnod mi 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:100a-48: rin chen sgron ma 'bar ba'i tshe //
T15TD4328E:100a-49: 'thor rlung tshogs kyis mi sod do //
T15TD4328E:100a-50: gya nom skyes bu'ang mi zhig ltar //
T15TD4328E:100a-51: ngan pa'i gnas su phyin 'gyur na //
T15TD4328E:100a-52: dur khrod kyi ni me bzhin du //
T15TD4328E:100a-54: g-yon can ngag 'jam smra ba la //
T15TD4328E:100a-55: mkhas pas nan tan ma brtags par /
T15TD4328E:100b-0: @100b yid brtan bya bar rud ma yin //
T15TD4328E:100b-1: rma bya yid 'ong sgra sgrogs par //
T15TD4328E:100b-2: zas su dug chen za ba bzhin //
T15TD4328E:100b-3: shes rab can gang dgra la yang //
T15TD4328E:100b-4: mdza' bshes lta bur sgrub byed pa //
T15TD4328E:100b-5: rgya mtsho bzhin du mi 'khrugs te //
T15TD4328E:100b-6: skye bo ngan pas drod mi zin //
T15TD4328E:100b-7: phyir rjed su ni lta ba dang //
T15TD4328E:100b-8: bag yod khong khro med pa dang //
T15TD4328E:100b-9: brtson 'grus brtan zhing mi g-yel ba'i //
T15TD4328E:100b-10: mi la dpal mgon nye bar gnas //
T15TD4328E:100b-11: gang zhig lan la mi re bar //
T15TD4328E:100b-12: sbyin pa gtod la sems spro ba //
T15TD4328E:100b-13: de ni snyan dang dal mkhas pa bzhin //
T15TD4328E:100b-14: mi yul 'di na grags pas mdzes //
T15TD4328E:100b-15: gang zhig dbang po bran lta bur //
T15TD4328E:100b-16: bka' bzhin rjes su mthun byed pa //
T15TD4328E:100b-17: rgya mtsho che la rin chen bzhin //
T15TD4328E:100b-18: de la 'dod dgu phun sum tshogs //
T15TD4328E:100b-19: bya ba ma yin mi byed cing //
T15TD4328E:100b-20: bshams ba mkhos su phebs pa dang //
T15TD4328E:100b-21: yul la 'dod pa thag bsrings pa'i //
T15TD4328E:100b-22: skyes bu mkhas pa sus mi bkur //
T15TD4328E:100b-23: mthu rtsal ldan pa'i khengs sems kyis //
T15TD4328E:100b-24: lugs kyi gdams ngag yongs mi spang //
T15TD4328E:100b-25: ru shing bzang po'i gzhu mchog kyang //
T15TD4328E:100b-26: rgyud med g-yu ngor ci zhig bya //
T15TD4328E:100b-27: g-yon cad rnams kyi gron can tshig / mdzangs pas legs pa ma brtags na //
T15TD4328E:100b-28: khong glu'i don rnams ma dbyang pa'i //
T15TD4328E:100b-29: ri dags gzhan gyis brlag par snang //
T15TD4328E:100b-30: mkhas pa rtag tu dgra la yang //
T15TD4328E:100b-31: mnyen nges can du bya dgos te //
T15TD4328E:100b-32: 'khri shing mnyen pos ljon shing la //
T15TD4328E:100b-33: 'khris nas rtse mor phyin te gnas //
T15TD4328E:100b-34: khong rgyud dogs pa tsam gyis 'dir //
T15TD4328E:100b-35: dgos dgu 'grub par mi gyur bas //
T15TD4328E:100b-36: yid kyis legs par rnam brtags te //
T15TD4328E:100b-37: ngag gis kun dang mthun par bya //
T15TD4328E:100b-38: ngag gis bzhams te smra bya zhing //
T15TD4328E:100b-39: res 'ga' byi l'i spyod pa'ang spyad //
T15TD4328E:100b-40: thabs dang ldan pa'i spyod pa la //
T15TD4328E:100b-41: mkhas pa su yang smod mi byad //
T15TD4328E:100b-42: rngon pa pus mo gnyis btsugs te //
T15TD4328E:100b-43: yan lag rnams kyi gum phag tu //
T15TD4328E:100b-44: byas te khon glu snyan len pas //
T15TD4328E:100b-45: ri dags sod par mi 'gyur ram //
T15TD4328E:100b-46: rgyas po'i bzhed pa mi sbyor ba //
T15TD4328E:100b-47: mkhas pas rtag tu 'bad de spang //
T15TD4328E:100b-48: sa bdag 'khor bcas thag ring zhes //
T15TD4328E:100b-49: khyad du gsad pa rung ma yin //
T15TD4328E:100b-50: lugs la / khas pa'i blon po yis //
T15TD4328E:100b-51: skye bo ma lus skyong byed pa'i //
T15TD4328E:100b-52: rgyal po gcig pu kho nas kyang //
T15TD4328E:100b-53: sa rnams la lus chom du phebs //
T15TD4328E:101a-2: legs nyes sems par byed pa yi //
T15TD4328E:101a-3: yul de rgyal po yod ces bya //
T15TD4328E:101a-4: de ltar de dag gtsor brtag go //
T15TD4328E:101a-5: gad na rgyal po 'bangs rnams kyis //
T15TD4328E:101a-6: legs nyes sems par mi byed pa //
T15TD4328E:101a-7: rgyal po de dag gtsug lag la //
T15TD4328E:101a-8: mkhas pa rnams kyis brten mi bya /
T15TD4328E:101a-9: yon tan ldan pa chung yang ni //
T15TD4328E:101a-11: zla ba shas tsam lus pa yang //
T15TD4328E:101a-12: drag po yis ni spyi la thogs //
T15TD4328E:101a-13: mkhas pa gang zhig bag med pa'i //
T15TD4328E:101a-14: gnas nas byol te 'bros pa dpa' //
T15TD4328E:101a-15: ri dags rgyal po mi gtsang ba'i //
T15TD4328E:101a-16: gnas nas 'dzur ba ga la ltar //
T15TD4328E:101a-17: legs nyes don chen mi sems par //
T15TD4328E:101a-18: mun sprul brtul ba dpa' ma yin //
T15TD4328E:101a-19: don med dpag tshad brgya yod pa'i //
T15TD4328E:101a-20: g-yang sar mchod ba ci cha yod //
T15TD4328E:101a-21: yon tan ldan yang thams cad du //
T15TD4328E:101a-22: grags chen thob par 'gyur ma yin //
T15TD4328E:101a-23: zla ba'i 'od zer bsil ba rnams //
T15TD4328E:101a-25: mjug tu skyor 'byin byed pa yi //
T15TD4328E:101a-26: snyan tshig mkhas pa sus mi bsngags //
T15TD4328E:101a-28: kha zas zhim po de su za //
T15TD4328E:101a-29: mkhas rnams rna bar mi snyan yang //
T15TD4328E:101a-30: phan tshig sman bzhin bsten par gyis //
T15TD4328E:101a-31: re zhig cig na de dag kyang //
T15TD4328E:101a-32: yang dag bdud rtsi lta bur 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101a-33: rigs pa'i don dang mi ldan pa'i //
T15TD4328E:101a-34: gzhung lugs gang zhig rtsom byed pa //
T15TD4328E:101a-36: sngags dang bral ba'i sbyin sreg bzhin //
T15TD4328E:101a-37: skyon dang yon tan 'di gnyis la //
T15TD4328E:101a-38: gcig tu mkhas par byas nas ni //
T15TD4328E:101a-39: dgos pa rtsom par byed pa gang //
T15TD4328E:101a-40: de la nyes pa rgyab kyis phyogs //
T15TD4328E:101a-41: snying la khong du dam bzung nas //
T15TD4328E:101a-42: bshes pa'i tshig ni ston byed pa //
T15TD4328E:101a-43: de dag mdzes pa ma yin te //
T15TD4328E:101a-44: srin bus zos pa'i sdong rul bzhin //
T15TD4328E:101a-45: gang dag tshig tu snyan smra zhing //
T15TD4328E:101a-46: snying la gzhan zhig 'jog byed pa //
T15TD4328E:101a-47: ri dags gzugs can stag lta bur //
T15TD4328E:101a-48: de bas yid brtan gnas ma yin //
T15TD4328E:101a-49: gson tshe grags pa dga' ba'i rgyu //
T15TD4328E:101a-51: de gnyis gcig kyang med pa ni //
T15TD4328E:101a-52: 'jig rten gnyis na ci zhig mi //
T15TD4328E:101a-53: gar skyes su ni zad ces te //
T15TD4328E:101a-54: rang gi brtson pa dor mi bya //
T15TD4328E:101b-0: 'bad pa @101b med par til dag las //
T15TD4328E:101b-1: til mar thob par 'gyur ma yin //
T15TD4328E:101b-2: kun la gnyen des mi bya ste //
T15TD4328E:101b-3: ha cang des pa gnod par 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101b-4: chu shing snying po med pa la //
T15TD4328E:101b-5: su zhig spyod par rtsom mi byed //
T15TD4328E:101b-6: gang zhig gtong phod blo ldan dpa' //
T15TD4328E:101b-7: tshig bden gtsang la byas pa gzo //
T15TD4328E:101b-8: de la rtag tu dpal grogs rnams //
T15TD4328E:101b-9: grib ma bzhin du rjes su 'brang //
T15TD4328E:101b-10: nags kyi glang chen zhags pa yis //
T15TD4328E:101b-11: bcings nas dbang du byed pa yang //
T15TD4328E:101b-12: thabs mkhas tshul la gnas pa yi //
T15TD4328E:101b-13: yon tan rnams kyi mthu stobs yin //
T15TD4328E:101b-14: rje dpon rang don lhur len pa //
T15TD4328E:101b-15: g-yog 'khor rten par mi byed de //
T15TD4328E:101b-16: sha la brkam pa'i seng ge la //
T15TD4328E:101b-17: wa skya re thag chad pa bzhin //
T15TD4328E:101b-18: gang zhig legs byas mi tshor ba //
T15TD4328E:101b-19: de la g-yog 'khor rten mi byed //
T15TD4328E:101b-20: tsha sgo can la legs rmos kyang //
T15TD4328E:101b-21: lo tog phun gsum tshogs mi 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101b-22: bdog pa ha cang spel ba yang //
T15TD4328E:101b-23: mjug tu rgud pas gdungs par 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101b-24: changs tshing mad dang ldan pa yis //
T15TD4328E:101b-25: sa phyogs tshig par 'gyur ba bzhin //
T15TD4328E:101b-26: gang zhig skye dgu 'tsho byed pa //
T15TD4328E:101b-27: de ni las nyid ston par byed //
T15TD4328E:101b-28: byis pa gnas sa ma byed par //
T15TD4328E:101b-29: nu zho 'thung ba su yis bsten //
T15TD4328E:101b-30: gang la zhe 'gras yod pa yi //
T15TD4328E:101b-31: dgra po de dang gzhar mi 'grogs //
T15TD4328E:101b-32: za bas bag tsam brjod pa yis //
T15TD4328E:101b-33: sgra gcan 'dzin gyis nyi ma zin //
T15TD4328E:101b-34: bya ba nyams kyis mi lcogs pa //
T15TD4328E:101b-35: gzhan gyis rbad kyang byar mi rung //
T15TD4328E:101b-37: me yi nang du su zhig mchod //
T15TD4328E:101b-38: ci nas bdag dmus ma byung ba'i //
T15TD4328E:101b-39: las kyis sbyor ba rnams bya ste //
T15TD4328E:101b-40: gsang bas 'di ni slob ma rnams //
T15TD4328E:101b-41: blon po nyid du 'gyur ram ci //
T15TD4328E:101b-42: phongs pa las gang byed pa ste //
T15TD4328E:101b-43: rnal mar 'dug pas byar mi rung //
T15TD4328E:101b-44: mdze can mer ni 'jug ces te //
T15TD4328E:101b-45: de ci gzhan gyi sman yin nam //
T15TD4328E:101b-47: gzhan du sdug bsngal mi 'gyur ba //
T15TD4328E:101b-49: shin tu yun ring dus su spyad //
T15TD4328E:101b-50: gang dag rgas rab mi bsten pa //
T15TD4328E:101b-51: de dag gtsug lag mkhas mi 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101b-52: gzu lums can gyi spyod pa rnams //
T15TD4328E:101b-53: dgos pa myur du nyams par 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101b-54: ha cang sog la zhen pa yi //
T15TD4328E:101b-55: bdog pa gzhan gyi don du 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:101b-56: sbrang mas 'bad de bsags pa yi //
T15TD4328E:102a-2: ngan pa rnams dang bshes 'dod pa //
T15TD4328E:102a-3: phung ba kho nar 'gyur bar zad //
T15TD4328E:102a-4: chu bos drung nas zos pa yis //
T15TD4328E:102a-6: phan skyabs che la brten na ni //
T15TD4328E:102a-7: chung yang btsan po nyid du 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:102a-8: ri rab btsan la brten pa'i bya //
T15TD4328E:102a-9: gser gyi mdog tu 'gyur zhes grags //
T15TD4328E:102a-10: khang bzangs zo mdog kya gyu med //
T15TD4328E:102a-11: klan ka mi tshol 'jar la phan //
T15TD4328E:102a-12: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu yod pa yi //
T15TD4328E:102a-13: grogs po rnams la lha yang dga' //
T15TD4328E:102a-14: mang po rnams ni 'jing dril nas //
T15TD4328E:102a-15: longs spyod phyir ni dbung 'chang ba //
T15TD4328E:102a-16: chags pa'i dbang gis phung 'gyur te //
T15TD4328E:102a-17: nas dang bral ba'i srin bzhin no //
T15TD4328E:102a-18: don rnams kun la mi gsal ba'i //
T15TD4328E:102a-19: ngan pa rnams ni 'dzings bsdongs nas //
T15TD4328E:102a-21: srin bu ra ba'i khar phyin bzhin //
T15TD4328E:102a-22: yul ngan bshes ni ngan pa dang //
T15TD4328E:102a-23: chung ma ngan dang 'khor ngan dang //
T15TD4328E:102a-24: rgyal po skye bo ngan spong ba //
T15TD4328E:102a-25: de dag rtag tu bde ba 'thob //
T15TD4328E:102a-26: skyes bu mkhas pa gcig rkya yang //
T15TD4328E:102a-28: ri dags rgyal po gcig pu yis //
T15TD4328E:102a-29: glang chen dregs khyu'i glad pa 'gems //
T15TD4328E:102a-30: mang po tshogs par gyur pa yi //
T15TD4328E:102a-31: nang na 'dug na gzhan dag gis //
T15TD4328E:102a-32: de 'dir zad ces mi rtsi ba //
T15TD4328E:102a-33: skyes bu tha shal yin snyam byed //
T15TD4328E:102a-34: rang don bsgrub par 'dod pa yis //
T15TD4328E:102a-35: rtag tu skyabs chen btsal bar bya //
T15TD4328E:102a-36: gang dag rgya mtsho cher phyin na //
T15TD4328E:102a-37: rang gi ming yang mi gleng ngo //
T15TD4328E:102a-38: rang bzhin ngan pa'i skye bo dang //
T15TD4328E:102a-39: shin tu mdza' bor byas kyang ni //
T15TD4328E:102a-40: mar me'i me lce tsha ba bzhin //
T15TD4328E:102a-41: nyid kyi rang bzhin mi 'dor ro //
T15TD4328E:102a-42: khon chen zhags pas phan tshun du //
T15TD4328E:102a-43: glags pa'i sems dang ldan pa rnams //
T15TD4328E:102a-45: khon chen de bzhin rjes su 'brang //
T15TD4328E:102a-46: dper na sprul dang ne'u le dang //
T15TD4328E:102a-47: bya rog 'ug pa ma he rta //
T15TD4328E:102a-48: tshe rabs gzhan la bsgrubs pa gang //
T15TD4328E:102a-49: de ci 'di la mi snang ngam //
T15TD4328E:102a-50: khro ba la ni brten rnams kyis //
T15TD4328E:102a-51: rang gi ngon yang mi rigs pas //
T15TD4328E:102a-52: mkhas pas rnam par ma brtags par //
T15TD4328E:102a-53: khro ba'i yus su mi bya'o //
T15TD4328E:102a-54: gang la bzod pa'i rang bzhin chu //
T15TD4328E:102a-55: khro ba'i me ni zhi byed pa //
T15TD4328E:102a-56: gdul ba'i thabs kyi mchog yod pa //
T15TD4328E:102a-57: de la dgra rnams ga la sdang //
T15TD4328E:102b-0: g-yung drung chos kyi go 'phang @102b mchog / legs pa'i gzhi la ma 'bad na //
T15TD4328E:102b-1: mthong dang ma mthong phun sum tshogs //
T15TD4328E:102b-2: chu yi chu bur bzhin du g-yo //
T15TD4328E:102b-3: snying la yod pa'i gsang tshig rnams //
T15TD4328E:102b-4: ngan pa rnams la spel mi bya //
T15TD4328E:102b-5: brang 'gro gdug pa khros pa bzhin //
T15TD4328E:102b-6: de la de yis gnod 'gyur srid //
T15TD4328E:102b-7: blo ldan gang zhig rtsom pa kun //
T15TD4328E:102b-8: chos gtsor byed pa'i dpal ldan pa //
T15TD4328E:102b-9: de la 'di dang gzhan du yang //
T15TD4328E:102b-10: bde bar 'gyur ba the tshom med //
T15TD4328E:102b-11: thabs mkhas cho gar ldan pa la //
T15TD4328E:102b-12: dgra rnams kyis ni rdzi mi 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:102b-13: cho ga rab tu sbyar legs na //
T15TD4328E:102b-14: dug kyang bdud rtsi nyid du 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:102b-15: dgra bcom phyogs dang bral ba yis //
T15TD4328E:102b-16: sems kyi gnod pa ga la spong //
T15TD4328E:102b-17: mtshon chag g-yul ngor cher zhugs pa //
T15TD4328E:102b-18: gdon mi za bar pham par 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:102b-19: grogs mi bdog pa 'gas kyang ni //
T15TD4328E:102b-20: dgra dpung gzhom par dka' bar 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:102b-21: tshang tshing nyung zad bsregs pa yi //
T15TD4328E:102b-22: me yang rlung la ltos dgos so //
T15TD4328E:102b-23: bdag dang gzhan la mi phan pa'i//
T15TD4328E:102b-24: phyug po bkren dang cis mi mtshungs //
T15TD4328E:102b-25: bud shing rnams dang phrad pa'i me //
T15TD4328E:102b-26: bud shing bsregs nas shi ba bzhin //
T15TD4328E:102b-27: gzhan gyis bzung ba'i bud med dag / rum du bcug ste nyal ba ni //
T15TD4328E:102b-28: lcags kyo med par glang po che //
T15TD4328E:102b-29: myos pa'i rgyab tu zhon pas thu //
T15TD4328E:102b-30: gang zhig rtag tu smad 'tshong ma'i //
T15TD4328E:102b-31: bud med rnams la gla 'jal ba //
T15TD4328E:102b-32: ston ka'i chu bo'i rtsa lag bzhin //
T15TD4328E:102b-33: de yi phun sum tshogs pa 'grib //
T15TD4328E:102b-34: blo ldan spyod lam zhi ba yi //
T15TD4328E:102b-35: lus kyi phan pa 'grub par byed //
T15TD4328E:102b-36: chu skyar spyod lam zhi ba yis //
T15TD4328E:102b-37: spyod pas nya rnams 'byin par byed //
T15TD4328E:102b-38: bdog pa rigs pas nyer bsgrubs shing //
T15TD4328E:102b-40: de ni 'jig rten thams cad kyis //
T15TD4328E:102b-41: spyi la me tog phreng bzhin bkur //
T15TD4328E:102b-44: nges kyang bdag nyid rtag par ni //
T15TD4328E:102b-45: yon tan rnams dang ldan par bya //
T15TD4328E:102b-46: gang zhig gzhan dag brlag bya zhes //
T15TD4328E:102b-47: khros pa'i me yis rang rgyud sreg / yon tan lhur len mi byed pa //
T15TD4328E:102b-48: de dag nam nam zhar phung //
T15TD4328E:102b-49: gang la rang gi shes rab med //
T15TD4328E:102b-50: de la bstan bcos ci byar yod //
T15TD4328E:102b-51: mig gnyis dang ni bral ba la //
T15TD4328E:102b-52: me long gis ni ci zhig bya //
T15TD4328E:102b-53: sbrul la 'o ma blud pa ni //
T15TD4328E:103a-2: ngan pa rnams la gdams pa yang //
T15TD4328E:103a-4: yon tan mchog ldan mi rnams ni //
T15TD4328E:103a-5: snying dang yid kyang 'dren par byed //
T15TD4328E:103a-6: mkhas pa yon tan lcags kyo yis //
T15TD4328E:103a-7: lam log glang chen drangs te bkol //
T15TD4328E:103a-10: dpa' bo tsham tshom med rtsom pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-11: mthu stobs can gyi dbang du 'gyur //
T15TD4328E:103a-13: 'di dang rang dbang med par 'dug / mthu rtsal ldan pa'i skyes mchog gis //
T15TD4328E:103a-14: lag nas drangs pa bzhin du spyod //
T15TD4328E:103a-15: gang zhig 'byung po thams cad la //
T15TD4328E:103a-16: rtag tu bdag dang 'drar byed pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-18: phun sum tshogs pa 'tshe ba med //
T15TD4328E:103a-19: btsan la mi 'gyur thabs mkhas shing //
T15TD4328E:103a-20: skye dgu rnams kyi gdung ba sel //
T15TD4328E:103a-21: kun la snying brtser bcas pa yi //
T15TD4328E:103a-22: mi dbang rnams ni sprin dang 'dra //
T15TD4328E:103a-23: gnam la sprin chen dal snyoms pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-24: sa la lo tog kun gyi gsos //
T15TD4328E:103a-25: bzod chen grib mar ldan pa yi //
T15TD4328E:103a-26: ljon shing skye dgu'i gdung ba sel //
T15TD4328E:103a-27: mi yi chos lugs legs spyad na //
T15TD4328E:103a-28: lha yul ba bgrod pa thag mi ring //
T15TD4328E:103a-29: lha dang mi yi them skas las //
T15TD4328E:103a-30: 'dzegs na thar pa gam na 'dug / don gyi bstan bcos lugs chen po //
T15TD4328E:103a-31: don mang phreng ba brgyus pa las //
T15TD4328E:103a-32: gces pa'i snying po mdor bsdus pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-33: shes rab brgya pa 'di yin no //
T15TD4328E:103a-34: gang zhig gzhan dring mi 'jog par //
T15TD4328E:103a-36: de yis phyogs 'di brtag byas pas //
T15TD4328E:103a-37: rang gzhan don du spyad pa spyod //
T15TD4328E:103a-38: byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang po rab tu dga' ba brnyes shing //
T15TD4328E:103a-39: chos kyi dbyings kun du 'gro ba'i don rtogs pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-40: de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes 'byung gnas 'od ces bya bar lung bstan pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-41: sangs rgyas gnyis par grags pa //
T15TD4328E:103a-42: slob dpon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa shes rab brgya pa zhes bya ba'i rab tu byed pa brgya pa rdzogs so /
T15TD4328E:103a-44: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po sarba dzny'a de ba dang //
T15TD4328E:103a-45: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba ban de dpal brtsegs kyis bsgyur cing /
T15TD4328E:103a-46: zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
